laced in the Eastern\\r\\nCaribbean. We have an agent there to look after the boat and handle\\r\\ncleaning, maintenance, between sailings. Generally we have excellent\\r\\nrelations with both marinas, and long standing contacts with skilled\\r\\nworkman in Trinidad.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe yacht has always been owned by a company (incorporated for that purpose), and therefore there is a complete set of financial records showing full maintenance records, and annual costs.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe yacht has been maintained to the highest standards.\\r\\n\\r\\nPhotos of Laurinda\\r\\n\",\"annual_costs\":\"Total annual costs were less than \\u00a315,000 in the years immediately up to 2007, but have been around \\u00a325-27,000 in the last 4 years as we have replaced or refurbished many items. \\r\\nWe will be replacing the water maker this summer. \\r\\nWe would anticipate costs for the next few years as \\u00a315-20,000 pa.\\r\\nCosts are paid in proportion to the ownership in the yacht\\r\\n\",\"are_you_selling_this_yacht_on_behalf_of_someone_else\":\"\",\"partner_1_details\":\"\",\"partner_2_details\":\"\",\"partner_3_details\":\"\",\"partner_4_details\":\"\",\"partner_5_details\":\"\",\"i_agree_to_yachtfractions_terms_and_conditions\":null}', NULL, 1347799675, 1357150510, '1', '0', '', 0, '1', 'NULL'),(66, 'Stormbird', '70\' Laurent Giles Cutter ', 'Sailing boat shares overseas', 'Northern Europe', 'Eire', 21, 200000, 0.333333, 1, 3, '{\"teaser\":\"S. Ireland - A Powerful blue water ketch designed by Laurent Giles with a comfortable deck saloon. Built 1979 by Jongert on a hull from Halmatic, recent complete and extensive rebuild from keel up to an as new condition. Designed with simple systems to allow ease of operation with a minimum crew. Currently based S. Ireland with plans to move to E. Med. Half or quarter shares also available\",\"seller_name\":\"\",\"first_name\":\"\",\"address_1\":\"\",\"address_2\":\"\",\"town\":\"\",\"postcodezipcode\":\"\",\"country\":\"\",\"telephone_wor